<claim-text>said target indicia positioned on said garment so as to correspond to the position of vulnerable target areas on said user when wearing said garment, said vulnerable target areas on said user vulnerable to forceful impacts, </claim-text>

<claim-text>said target indicia including target indicia on limb-covering portion of said garment so as to correspond to vulnerable areas of said vulnerable target areas on said limbs of said user. </claim-text>

