<paragraph id="P-0029" lvl="0"><number>&lsqb;0029&rsqb;</number> <cross-reference target="DRAWINGS">FIG. 9</cross-reference> is a detail view of the pivot assembly seen in detail circle D of <cross-reference target="DRAWINGS">FIG. 5</cross-reference>; </paragraph>

<paragraph id="P-0030" lvl="0"><number>&lsqb;0030&rsqb;</number> <cross-reference target="DRAWINGS">FIG. 10</cross-reference> is a detail view of the pivot assembly seen in detain circle E of <cross-reference target="DRAWINGS">FIG. 5</cross-reference>; </paragraph>

<paragraph id="P-0031" lvl="0"><number>&lsqb;0031&rsqb;</number> <cross-reference target="DRAWINGS">FIG. 11</cross-reference> is a detail view of the pivot assembly seen in detail circle F of <cross-reference target="DRAWINGS">FIG. 5</cross-reference>; </paragraph>

