<paragraph id="P-0044" lvl="0"><number>&lsqb;0044&rsqb;</number> As will be noted from Table 2, for bends formed using the described rotary bending apparatus, the ratio of the degree of bend applied to that of the formed bend is generally between about 1.25 and 1.35 and, is most preferably between about and 1.30.  
<table-cwu id="TABLE-US-00003">
<number>3</number>
